org.jmisb.api.klv.st0601

Class UasDatalinkAngle

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jmisb.api.klv.st0601.UasDatalinkAngle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IKlvValue, IUasDatalinkValue
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PlatformAngleOfAttack, PlatformPitchAngle, PlatformSideslipAngle

    public abstract class UasDatalinkAngle
extends Object
implements IUasDatalinkValue
    Generic angle (used by ST 0601 items 6, 50 and 52).

    From ST:

    Map (-2^15-1)..(2^15-1) to +/-20. Use -2^15 as an "out of range" indicator. -2^15 = 0x8000.

    Resolution: ~610 micro degrees
